desc: Handmade sterling silver jewellery inspired by nature - created to encourage your soul to shine. Sharing spiritual connections & inspiration for each piece of jewellery. Entirely made by hand with recycled sterling silver and seaglass. Inspired by natural wonders of the world Handmade & designed in Australia by Chelsea

layout.text: Glass which has being disposed as waste into the ocean, being tumbled and shaped in the sea landing on the shoreline with a story to tell waiting to be found as treasure. May the seaglass within this collection inspire you to reduce your impact on the environment while encouraging you to travel & share your unique journeys along the way.
